        <mxCell id="footer" value="ONE BRAIN PATTERN, THREE SOVEREIGN INSTANCES — the same 7-agent topology is deployed in DK (northeurope), SE (swedencentral), NO (norwayeast). Per-country isolation at the model deployment, the agent registry, the evaluation suite, the knowledge base. Sovereignty exception: gpt-realtime is not yet GA in norwayeast — NO voice orchestrator uses SE hub's deployment under Microsoft EU Data Boundary + Nordic-DPA cooperation; citizen audio + transcripts persist only in NO." style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=10;fontStyle=2;fillColor=none;fontColor=#475569;" vertex="1" parent="1">
